{"tid":2169274,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"M到頭幾日比男朋友内射","createTime":"2020-08-22T11:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T15:17:21.000Z","uid":1369,"like":47,"dislike":767,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"b14fb07c874b8ad947b0198bfdb874d0eb8d89bb","tid":2169274,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"小妹17歲個幾月前先同男友一齊破處，而家大家協定每星期只可以做愛一次，同埋要用condom，第一次大家無用condom內射有啲擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住兩星期前M到第二日比男友唔用套叫佢出面射但忍唔到內射咗，我睇咗啲資料話M到頭幾日內射好難有BB，男友問我可唔可以黎M果次做愛可以比佢唔用套，唔知應唔應承佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位哥哥有咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋想請教女仔做過第一次破處後，會唔會有成日想做愛的心態，唔知點解做左幾次之後，好似成日都好想快啲到下一次同男友曳曳，好enjoy同男友曳曳果陣對我果份溫柔，平時拍拖行街都無果種寧捨warm同被愛的感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb03dc85fef30440fc190bd9f1de3714331ae8d","tid":2169274,"uid":1977,"like":204,"dislike":16,"score":188,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"順便洗下隻臭閪"},{"pid":"92d18c5e5bf1452f90d24a4c6dfc95c3cff848c1","tid":2169274,"uid":206382,"like":119,"dislike":11,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"做乜咁唔錫身呀sis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543123341e4c28ea55280585214e174508f2426c","tid":2169274,"uid":50193,"like":529,"dislike":4,"score":525,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"兩個男人點會有BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cc1f0e6ed91c88fa71f5ecab562aafdff3e9c0","tid":2169274,"uid":183358,"like":217,"dislike":1,"score":216,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d99c85efd55d026dfb0d7880e892ebb988f977c1","tid":216927