" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"做好心理準備 個bb你要唔要"},{"pid":"c3eaec47e8be11d5043521ee32f6f955c43d0d07","tid":2169274,"uid":206382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c726a239a26dce03a250d931aeaf0901080bf13","tid":2169274,"uid":365454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"番波台啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:17:29.000Z","msg":"呢到咪波台"},{"pid":"bc74eafdd7b338af27bbfbb21132d383804c074a","tid":2169274,"uid":311499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"若果對方是男性同時是 HIV 陽性：<br />\n<br />\n👉 無套陰道交，女方感染機率 0.08% (1/1250)<br />\n👉 無套肛交，接受方感染機率 <br />\n※無內射 0.65% (1/154)<br />\n※有內射 1.43% (1/70)<br />\n<br />\n同時存在其他性病風險，如梅毒、淋病、皰疹2型、椰菜花、衣原體、乙肝、丙肝等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc700c3896b5274fe108bb418c8018de14c567a","tid":2169274,"uid":87192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"你都幾撚蠢"},{"pid":"a68e871fb7ea5647f5cba75016ca8dfb0141a878","tid":2169274,"uid":127753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"男人老狗叫小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c1c2de4596d192ead3d762576c5f8471e41ba2","tid":2169274,"uid":231886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYAZWeZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYAZWeZ.png&h=e872ce1e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"red\">肛交口爆會有bb？</span>"},{"pid":"1492b30759aec996a76cc162b2800cce21696561","tid":2169274,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:40:4